WEBVTT

00:37.037 --> 00:38.995
[woman] I CAN'T BELIEVE
THEY CAN'T FIND HIM.

00:39.082 --> 00:40.736
HE'S JUST NEVER DONE
THIS BEFORE.

00:45.654 --> 00:48.831
ANYTHING ELSE YOU GUYS HEAR,
LET US KNOW, OKAY?THANK YOU.

00:52.530 --> 00:54.706
KID'S NAME'S CODY ELKINS,
16 YEARS OLD.

00:54.793 --> 00:56.317
REPORTED MISSING
A COUPLE DAYS AGO.

00:56.404 --> 00:59.102
CALLED US WHEN THE LOCAL
POLICEMEN FOUND HIS SHOE

00:59.189 --> 01:02.192
TWO STREETS AWAY IN A GUTTER.
WAITING ON THE D.N.A.

01:02.279 --> 01:05.456
WE FIGURE IT'S AN ABDUCTION,
POTENTIAL HOMICIDE,
MAKING IT A CBI CASE.

01:05.543 --> 01:07.545
THE PARENTS ARE MICHAEL
AND JANICE, BOTH CLEAN.

01:07.632 --> 01:09.634
THEY HAVE ANOTHER SON
NAMED BRAD, 14.

01:09.721 --> 01:12.159
THEY OWN A FLOWER SHOP HERE.
CHO'S WITH 'EM NOW.

01:12.246 --> 01:14.813
LET'S GO.

01:14.900 --> 01:17.816
[door bells jingle]THINK I'LL JUST
WAIT OUT HERE.

01:17.903 --> 01:19.209
[Lisbon] THAT'S FINE.

01:55.680 --> 01:56.725
OH, WHAT?

01:58.683 --> 02:00.598
HEY, DUDE.CUTE BIKE.

02:00.685 --> 02:03.166
WHAT YOU DOING?WOW.

02:03.253 --> 02:06.517
YOU BOYS GOTTA BE PRETTY
ANXIOUS TO SEE SOMETHING
TO RIDE THIS, HUH?

02:06.604 --> 02:10.042
HUH?YOU DIDN'T RIDE A PINK BIKE
TO COME TO THE STORE?

02:10.130 --> 02:12.306
WHAT'D YOU COME TO SEE?NOTHING.

02:12.393 --> 02:14.134
REALLY?LET'S GO, CLYDE.

02:14.221 --> 02:16.440
WHERE'S CODY ELKINS?I DON'T KNOW.

02:16.527 --> 02:19.487
I KNOW YOU GUYS KNOW
WHERE HE'S.
DON'T HAVE TELL OUT LOUD.

02:19.574 --> 02:23.055
JUST LOOK IN THE DIRECTION.
THAT WAY?

02:23.143 --> 02:26.102
WHY DID YOU DO THAT?

02:26.189 --> 02:27.799
THANK YOU.

02:27.886 --> 02:29.932
HERE'S YOUR BIKE.

02:30.019 --> 02:31.020
BE SAFE.

02:33.457 --> 02:35.024
[door bells jingle]

02:35.111 --> 02:36.765
CHO'S GONNA BRING
THE ELKINS HOME.

02:44.642 --> 02:47.341
I HAVE A PRETTY GOOD IDEA
WHERE CODY ELKINS IS.

02:47.428 --> 02:48.777
SHARING IS GOOD.

02:53.956 --> 02:55.175
[crow caws]

02:55.262 --> 02:57.046
WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
HE'S HERE?

02:57.133 --> 02:59.918
BECAUSE THOSE KIDS GAVE IT AWAY.
PLUS THEY SMELLED
LIKE EUCALYPTUS.

03:00.005 --> 03:02.573
BUT THERE'S EUCALYPTUS TREES
ALL OVER AROUND HERE.CROWS.

03:02.660 --> 03:06.621
SO?CROWS ARE CARRION BIRDS.
THEY LIKE DEAD THINGS.

03:06.708 --> 03:08.362
[cawing]

03:30.862 --> 03:32.081
OH, JEEZ.

03:42.439 --> 03:43.614
POOR KID.

04:02.677 --> 04:04.896
WHAT DOES IT MEAN?

04:04.983 --> 04:06.985
BLACK MAGIC.

04:07.072 --> 04:08.639
SACRIFICE.

04:08.726 --> 04:11.816
BUT THERE'S NO SUCH THING
AS BLACK MAGIC.

04:11.903 --> 04:13.296
WELL, SOMEBODY DISAGREES.

04:27.919 --> 04:30.313
♪♪

04:38.365 --> 04:40.323
NUMBER ONE, WE'RE LOOKING
FOR A MURDER WEAPON.

04:40.410 --> 04:43.108
ANYTHING YOU FIND, ANYTHING
AT ALL, TAG IT AND BAG IT.

04:43.195 --> 04:44.458
THANKS, GUYS.

04:49.463 --> 04:50.725
WAIT A SECOND.

04:59.516 --> 05:01.431
[Lisbon]
WHEN DID YOU LAST SEE CODY?

05:01.518 --> 05:04.478
[Michael] FRIDAY NIGHT,
AFTER THE GAME.

05:04.565 --> 05:07.524
UH, CODY PLAYS WIDE RECEIVER
FOR HIS HIGH SCHOOL TEAM.

05:07.611 --> 05:10.484
UH, THEY GOT BLOWN OUT
PRETTY GOOD THAT NIGHT.

05:10.571 --> 05:13.574
BUT, UH, IT'S
A PRETTY GOOD TEAM THIS YEAR.

05:13.661 --> 05:14.923
IT'S NATIONALLY RANKED.

05:15.010 --> 05:17.969
WHEN EXACTLY DID YOU
SEE HIM LAST ON FRIDAY?

05:18.056 --> 05:20.058
UH, WHEN HE WENT TO BED.

05:20.145 --> 05:22.844
WE WERE, ALL THREE OF US,
OUT EARLY THE NEXT MORNING.

05:22.931 --> 05:26.848
WHEN WE CAME BACK
THAT AFTERNOON, CODY WAS GONE.

05:26.935 --> 05:29.938
HE WAS, UH, SUPPOSED TO MEET
HIS COACH THE NEXT MORNING

05:30.025 --> 05:32.723
FOR, UH, SOME EXTRA PRACTICE,
BUT HE NEVER SHOWED UP.

05:32.810 --> 05:38.381
[Janice sniffles]BRAD.

05:38.468 --> 05:41.297
AND THAT FRIDAY NIGHT,
WHAT WAS HIS STATE OF MIND?

05:41.384 --> 05:43.604
HE WAS FINE. [sniffles]

05:43.691 --> 05:47.216
FINE.HE WAS A LITTLE UPSET
WITH HIMSELF ABOUT THE GAME.

05:47.303 --> 05:49.827
HE'D, UH, MADE SOME
MENTAL ERRORS, YOU KNOW?

05:49.914 --> 05:53.222
UH, COACH D.
GOT ON HIM PRETTY GOOD.

05:53.309 --> 05:55.833
CODY KIND OF PUSHED BACK
A LITTLE BIT, I GUESS.

05:55.920 --> 05:58.532
THEY HAD A FIGHT?YOU COULD SAY.

05:58.619 --> 06:01.012
IT'S NOTHING SERIOUS--
LOCKER ROOM STUFF,

06:01.099 --> 06:03.406
A LITTLE SHOUTING.

06:03.493 --> 06:06.627
CODY JUST WANTED TO DO BETTER.

06:06.714 --> 06:09.151
HOW DID HE DIE?THERE WERE INDICATIONS
AROUND THE BODY

06:09.238 --> 06:11.283
OF SOME KIND OF
BLACK MAGIC RITUAL.

06:11.371 --> 06:13.329
NOW DID HE HAVE ANY FRIENDS
OR ACQUAINTANCES

06:13.416 --> 06:17.159
WHO WERE INVOLVED
IN THAT KIND OF THING?OH, MY GOD.

06:17.246 --> 06:18.943
IT WAS HER.

06:19.030 --> 06:21.032
[Michael] OF COURSE.WHO'S THIS?

06:21.119 --> 06:23.339
TAMZIN DOVE.

06:23.426 --> 06:26.647
SHE'S INTO ALL THAT
BLACK MAGIC CRAP.

06:26.734 --> 06:29.998
SHE'S...
CLAIMS TO BE A WITCH.

06:30.085 --> 06:31.303
SAYS SHE HAS POWERS.

06:33.175 --> 06:35.699
AND DID SHE HAVE SOME SORT
OF RESENTMENT TOWARD CODY?

06:35.786 --> 06:39.529
UH-HUH. ABOUT A-A WEEK AGO,
SHE, UH...

06:39.616 --> 06:42.097
SHE CLAIMED THAT
CODY STOLE HER CAT.

06:42.184 --> 06:44.229
DID HE?NO.

06:44.316 --> 06:45.753
OF COURSE NOT.

06:45.840 --> 06:49.626
BUT SHE PUT A SPELL
ON HIM IN REVENGE.

06:49.713 --> 06:51.672
A SPELL?
WHAT KIND OF SPELL?

06:51.759 --> 06:53.935
I DON'T KNOW,
BUT SHE ACTUALLY CALLED

06:54.022 --> 06:55.545
AND SAID THAT SHE'D DONE IT.

06:55.632 --> 06:57.155
THAT MUST HAVE BEEN WORRISOME.

06:57.242 --> 07:01.029
AT THE TIME, CODY THOUGHT
IT WAS KIND OF FUNNY.

07:01.116 --> 07:03.988
I MEAN,
SHE'S A-A GEEK, YOU KNOW?

07:04.075 --> 07:06.861
I THINK THAT'S WHY WE DIDN'T
THINK ABOUT HER RIGHT AWAY.

07:06.948 --> 07:08.428
WHERE CAN WE FIND
TAMZIN DOVE?

07:10.604 --> 07:12.127
THINGS ARE GETTING
WEIRD ALREADY.

07:12.214 --> 07:14.303
WE'RE OFF TO SEE A WITCH.OH.

07:14.390 --> 07:16.653
BE CAREFUL.YEAH, YEAH.

07:16.740 --> 07:18.742
YOU FIND ANYTHING USEFUL THERE?NOTHING--

07:18.829 --> 07:20.918
NO MURDER WEAPON,
NOT A LOT OF BLOOD.

07:21.005 --> 07:22.616
LOOKS LIKE HE WAS
KILLED ELSEWHERE.

07:22.703 --> 07:25.445
M.E. ESTIMATES THAT HE DIED
EARLY SATURDAY MORNING,

07:25.532 --> 07:27.969
THE CAUSE BEING SEVERAL BLOWS

07:28.056 --> 07:29.579
with a heavy, blunt object

07:29.666 --> 07:31.668
like a crowbar
or a pipe, maybe.

07:31.755 --> 07:34.584
I WANT YOU TWO TO TALK
TO CODY'S FOOTBALL COACH.

07:34.671 --> 07:37.152
He and the kid had a fight
on Friday night.

07:37.239 --> 07:39.894
They were supposed to meet up
on Saturday morning.GOT IT.

07:39.981 --> 07:41.678
WE GOT THE FOOTBALL BEAT.ALRIGHT.

07:51.122 --> 07:52.210
LOOK--A GOAT.

07:52.297 --> 07:54.169
GOATS ARE SIGNS OF SATAN.

07:54.256 --> 07:57.085
SO PETTING ZOOS ARE, LIKE,
GATEWAYS TO HELL?[rings doorbell]

07:57.172 --> 07:58.347
PRETTY MUCH.

08:00.610 --> 08:02.525
OOH, LOOK, ANOTHER BAD SIGN.

08:04.396 --> 08:05.789
[Lisbon] OOH.

08:07.878 --> 08:09.010
[rings doorbell]

08:18.933 --> 08:20.891
BOO.WHOA!

08:20.978 --> 08:23.241
YOU SHOULDN'T JOKE AROUND
ABOUT THIS KIND OF STUFF.

08:24.895 --> 08:26.549
IT DOESN'T LOOK
LIKE ANYBODY'S HOME.

08:26.636 --> 08:30.205
NOT MUCH SECURITY
FOR A SERVANT OF THE DEVIL.

08:30.292 --> 08:33.208
I COULD PICK THAT LOCK WITH THIS
IN ABOUT FIVE SECONDS.

08:33.295 --> 08:35.732
WE'LL WAIT.

08:35.819 --> 08:39.606
DON'T LOOK NOW,
BUT WE SHOULD GRAB ONE
OF THOSE KIDS AND TALK TO 'EM.

08:41.651 --> 08:44.524
DAMN.ARE THEY THE SAME KIDS
FROM THE ELKINS SHOP?

08:44.611 --> 08:45.525
YES.

08:52.227 --> 08:55.665
[whistle blows][man] LET'S SEE SOME HUSTLE
OUT THERE NOW!

08:55.752 --> 08:57.928
IT'S A TRAGEDY.
HIS WHOLE LIFE AHEAD OF HIM.

08:58.015 --> 08:59.147
GREAT KID, TOO.

09:01.497 --> 09:03.064
GO, GO, GO, GO, GO, GO!

09:03.151 --> 09:06.850
VINSON, YOU MANATEE!
MOVE YOUR LARD BUTT DOWNFIELD!

09:10.158 --> 09:12.508
GREAT KID.
GOOD VALUES, GOOD HABITS.

09:12.595 --> 09:15.293
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO MEET
WITH HIM SATURDAY MORNING?THAT'S RIGHT.

09:15.380 --> 09:18.079
9:00 A.M., FOR SOME
SERIOUS FUMBLE PREVENTION REPS.

09:18.166 --> 09:21.952
HE NEVER SHOWED.YOU AND HE HAD SERIOUS WORDS
FRIDAY NIGHT, RIGHT?

09:22.039 --> 09:25.042
[sighs] YEAH, CODY HAD
A SHAMEFUL GAME--

09:25.129 --> 09:27.871
ZERO T.D.s, TWO FUMBLES
AND FIVE BLOWN ROUTES--

09:27.958 --> 09:30.787
A PERSONAL FOUL
THAT COST US 15 YARDS.

09:30.874 --> 09:33.050
HE LET HIMSELF DOWN
AND LET HIS TEAM DOWN.

09:33.137 --> 09:35.096
HIS M.O. LATELY.
THAT'S WHY WE'RE MEETING

09:35.183 --> 09:37.446
ON SATURDAY MORNING,
TO GET HIM BACK ON TRACK.

09:37.533 --> 09:40.057
"SHAMEFUL"--THAT'S KIND OF
HARSH, ISN'T IT?

09:40.144 --> 09:41.885
I RUN A REALITY-BASED
PROGRAM HERE.

09:41.972 --> 09:44.496
IF YOU WANNA HEAR MALARKEY,
TRY THE ENGLISH DEPARTMENT.

09:44.584 --> 09:49.023
TILLIS! I CAN SEE YOU,
TILLIS! I CAN SEE YOU.

09:49.110 --> 09:51.199
WHAT DID CODY
HAVE TO SAY IN REPLY?

09:51.286 --> 09:53.897
WHAT I DISCUSSED WITH CODY
IS NOBODY'S BUSINESS.

09:53.984 --> 09:56.683
PEOPLE'VE NO IDEA
HOW IT'S BETWEEN
A COACH AND HIS TEAM.

09:56.770 --> 09:58.641
WE HAVE AN IDEA.I DOUBT IT.

09:58.728 --> 10:00.600
WE LOOKED INTO YOUR HISTORY,
MR. DIETER.

10:00.687 --> 10:03.167
FIVE YEARS AGO, YOU LOST
A HIGH SCHOOL COACHING JOB

10:03.254 --> 10:07.302
IN OREGON FOR INAPPROPRIATE
PHYSICAL CONTACT WITH STUDENTS.WAIT A MINUTE.

10:07.389 --> 10:10.131
YOU MAKE THAT SOUND LIKE I'M
A SEX MOLESTER OR SOMETHIN'.

10:10.218 --> 10:13.221
I SMACKED A COUPLE OF KIDS
BECAUSE THEY NEEDED
AN ATTITUDE ADJUSTMENT.

10:13.308 --> 10:16.311
THEIR PANTYWAIST PARENTS
MADE AN ISSUE OF IT.THAT'S OKAY THEN?

10:16.398 --> 10:18.966
IT'S FOOTBALL.ACTUALLY,
THAT'S ASSAULT ON A MINOR.

10:19.053 --> 10:21.621
THERE WERE NO CHARGES FILED.BUT YOU HAD TO RESIGN.

10:21.708 --> 10:25.625
NO. NO, I CHOSE TO RESIGN.WITH A PROMISE TO TAKE
ANGER MANAGEMENT CLASS.

10:25.712 --> 10:28.236
36 HOURS' WORTH.
I DID MY TIME.

10:28.323 --> 10:31.456
BORED THE RAGE RIGHT OUT OF ME.

10:31.543 --> 10:34.024
ASK ALL THE QUESTIONS YOU WANT.
I'M NOT HIDING ANYTHING.

10:34.111 --> 10:37.332
WE NEED TO SEARCH THE GYM
AND THE LOCKER ROOMS.DO WHATEVER.

10:37.419 --> 10:41.989
FRANK! FRANK, YOU NEED
TO PULL AROUND HIM,
AND YOU NEED TO GET UPFIELD.

10:42.076 --> 10:46.341
NO, YOUR STRONG SIDE TACKLE
SHOULD DO THAT.
HE'S GOT THE BETTER FIRST SET,

10:46.428 --> 10:48.386
AND YOUR TIGHT END'S
JUMPING HIS ROUTE.

10:55.350 --> 10:57.569
QUICK HANDS,
THINK FAST.

10:57.657 --> 10:59.702
HIT ME. I'M OPEN.UH, NO.

10:59.789 --> 11:04.098
WHAT KIND OF COACH'S KID
ARE YOU? YOUR DADDY
WOULD BE ASHAMED.

11:04.185 --> 11:06.100
FINE. GO LONG.OH!

11:07.754 --> 11:09.277
OH, NICE!

11:15.849 --> 11:18.025
HEY, CHECK THIS OUT.INTERESTING.

11:23.204 --> 11:24.988
LET'S GET THIS TO FORENSICS.

11:32.474 --> 11:34.345
OKAY, BOSS.

11:34.432 --> 11:37.131
MINELLI SAYS WE CAN GO IN.
THE WARRANT'S ON ITS WAY.

11:37.218 --> 11:38.436
LET'S DO THIS.

11:38.523 --> 11:40.221
BET YOU CAN'T DO IT
IN FIVE...

11:43.006 --> 11:44.225
NEVER MIND.

11:48.185 --> 11:50.187
WHAT'S WRONG?I'LL WAIT OUT HERE.

11:50.274 --> 11:52.624
WHY?

11:52.712 --> 11:54.539
ALRIGHT, I'LL GO IN,
BUT YOU FIRST.

12:04.724 --> 12:05.855
HELLO.

12:05.942 --> 12:07.161
UH... HELLO.

12:12.732 --> 12:14.603
WELCOME.

12:14.690 --> 12:18.041
YOU MUST BE THE CBI.
PLEASE SIT DOWN.

12:18.128 --> 12:20.652
THANK YOU.WHY DIDN'T YOU
JUST LET US IN?

12:20.740 --> 12:23.743
IF I HAD, I WOULDN'T HAVE
THE UPPER HAND, NOW WOULD I?

12:23.830 --> 12:26.920
SO YOU WERE EXPECTING US.OF COURSE.

12:27.007 --> 12:29.531
I HEARD WHAT WAS DONE
TO CODY ELKINS.

12:29.618 --> 12:31.315
THEY USED A PENTACLE
AND A FLAME,

12:31.402 --> 12:35.015
MADE IT LOOK LIKE
WITCHCRAFT--WICCA.

12:35.102 --> 12:36.494
NATURALLY, YOU'D COME TO ME.

12:38.670 --> 12:40.368
I'M THE ONLY WITCH IN TOWN.

12:49.507 --> 12:51.335
THOSE DETAILS ABOUT THAT--
NO, THANK YOU--PENTACLES,

12:51.422 --> 12:53.555
AND THE CANDLES
WEREN'T MADE PUBLIC.

12:53.642 --> 12:55.557
HOW DID YOU KNOW ABOUT THEM?YES, PLEASE.

12:55.644 --> 12:57.646
FRIENDS.

12:57.733 --> 13:00.127
SO YOUR FRIENDS WERE INVOLVED
IN CODY'S DEATH?

13:00.214 --> 13:02.607
NO.ARE THESE FRIENDS SMALL
WITH LONG HAIR?

13:02.694 --> 13:04.435
THE LEADER'S NAME IS CLYDE?

13:04.522 --> 13:07.047
HE HAS A SISTER
WITH A PINK BIKE?

13:07.134 --> 13:08.439
YES, THAT'S THEM.

13:08.526 --> 13:11.225
SO YOU'RE FRIENDS
WITH A LOT OF KIDS THEN.

13:11.312 --> 13:12.922
YES, KIDS...

13:13.009 --> 13:16.360
THEY LIKE MYSTERY
AND DARKNESS,

13:16.447 --> 13:21.017
AND I LIKE KIDS.WHAT DO THEIR PARENTS
HAVE TO SAY ABOUT THAT?

13:21.104 --> 13:24.760
THE KIDS THAT COME HERE
COME BECAUSE THEIR PARENTS
DON'T GIVE A HOOT.

13:24.847 --> 13:27.197
BUT THEY HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH CODY'S DEATH,

13:27.284 --> 13:29.112
NOR THE PENTACLE
AND THE CANDLES.

13:29.199 --> 13:31.419
WHAT WERE THEY DOING
IN THE WOODS, THEN?

13:31.506 --> 13:33.813
PICKING HERBS FOR ME.HERBS?

13:33.900 --> 13:36.641
FENUGREEK,
WILD ROSES, NETTLES.

13:38.252 --> 13:39.340
PLEASE.

13:46.782 --> 13:49.959
I MAKE AND SELL WICCA
HEALING POWDERS ON THE INTERNET.

13:50.046 --> 13:52.048
YOU SHOULD CHECK OUT
MY WEBSITE.

13:52.135 --> 13:56.270
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL THE POLICE
YOUR FRIENDS FOUND A BODY?WHAT FOR?

13:56.357 --> 14:00.752
I KNEW THE EARTH
AND THE RAIN AND THE ANIMALS
WOULD TAKE CARE OF CODY.

14:00.840 --> 14:03.494
YOU CAN'T HELP HIM.IT'S TRUE. WE CAN'T,

14:03.581 --> 14:07.063
BUT WHAT WE CANDO IS FIND
AND PUNISH THE PEOPLE
WHO MURDERED HIM.

14:07.150 --> 14:08.673
THERE'S NO NEED.

14:08.760 --> 14:12.155
CODY DESERVED TO DIE.
HE WAS A BAD PERSON.

14:12.242 --> 14:16.507
HE STOLE AND TORTURED
AND KILLED MY CAT.

14:16.594 --> 14:19.032
I SAW HIM TAKE IT.WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

14:19.119 --> 14:21.164
FEAR, I GUESS.

14:21.251 --> 14:23.471
THAT'S JUST THE WAY IT IS
WITH THE COWEN.

14:23.558 --> 14:27.562
THEY LIVE IN FEAR.THE COWEN?

14:27.649 --> 14:31.131
THOSE WHO ARE NOT WICCA.
THOSE WHO UNBELIEVE OUR POWERS.

14:31.218 --> 14:33.133
WHAT POWERS ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT, EXACTLY?

14:33.220 --> 14:37.137
A WITCH IS SIMPLY
A HIGH PRIESTESS OF THE WICCA.

14:37.224 --> 14:39.922
WE WORSHIP THE HORNED GOD
AND THE TRIPLE GODDESS.

14:40.009 --> 14:43.230
WE'RE HEALERS MOSTLY,
BUT WE HAVE THE MAGIC ALSO,

14:43.317 --> 14:46.059
WHEN NEEDED--
SPELLS AND SO FORTH.

14:46.146 --> 14:49.758
DID YOU PUT A SPELL
ON CODY ELKINS?I DID.

14:49.845 --> 14:52.195
I PUT A KILLING SPELL ON HIM.MM.

14:52.282 --> 14:54.415
I'D DONE THE SPELL
SEVERAL TIMES BEFORE,

14:54.502 --> 14:57.766
BUT THIS IS THE FIRST TIME
IT'S WORKED.

14:57.853 --> 15:00.638
WHAT DOES
THE SPELLING INVOLVE?

15:00.725 --> 15:02.118
WHAT DO YOU DO, EXACTLY?

15:06.296 --> 15:09.517
WHY AM I HERE?EXPLAIN TO US
WHY FORENSICS TELLS US

15:09.604 --> 15:13.173
THAT YOUR BLOOD WAS FOUND
ALL OVER A T-SHIRT
WE FOUND IN CODY'S LOCKER.

15:13.260 --> 15:15.175
I TOLD YOU,
WE HAD AN ARGUMENT.

15:15.262 --> 15:19.179
OH, SO NOW YOU'RE SAYING
YOU HAD AN ACTUAL FISTFIGHT?
YOU DREW BLOOD?

15:19.266 --> 15:21.790
YEAH.
IT WAS NO BIG DEAL.
I CHEWED HIM OUT.

15:21.877 --> 15:24.184
HE GOT MAD, AND
TOOK A COUPLE OF SWINGS.

15:24.271 --> 15:27.187
LAID OUT BY A KID, HUH?IT WAS A LUCKY PUNCH.

15:27.274 --> 15:31.147
YOUR OWN STUDENT BEATS YOU
AND YOU DON'T TELL ANYONE?IT WAS NO BIG DEAL.

15:31.234 --> 15:34.846
OR YOU FIGURED YOU'LL GET EVEN
WITH HIM TOMORROW
SO BEST KEEP IT QUIET?

15:34.934 --> 15:39.155
NO. NO.
I WAS TOO EMBARRASSED.

15:39.242 --> 15:41.810
PEOPLE DON'T KNOW THE KID
IS A FREAKING NUT BAG.

15:41.897 --> 15:43.333
MAKES ME LOOK BAD
EITHER WAY,

15:43.420 --> 15:45.509
SO I JUST PRETENDED
IT DIDN'T HAPPEN.

15:45.596 --> 15:48.730
HE HIT YOU FIRST--
HIS OWN COACH?

15:48.817 --> 15:50.123
I TOLD YOU--A NUT BAG.

15:50.210 --> 15:51.820
WELL, THAT'S NOT
WHAT WE'VE HEARD.

15:51.907 --> 15:54.736
ASK DANIEL BROWN.
HE'S A GOOD FRIEND OF CODY'S.

15:54.823 --> 15:58.044
LAST MONTH CODY GOT MAD
OVER A CARD GAME OR SOMETHING.

15:58.131 --> 16:00.655
BEAT DANNO UNCONSCIOUS.
HAD TO BE DRAGGED OFF OF HIM.

16:00.742 --> 16:02.439
DON'T KNOW WHY DANNO
DIDN'T PRESS CHARGES.

16:02.526 --> 16:04.572
DANIEL BROWN?YEAH.

16:11.709 --> 16:13.146
KILLING SPELLS ARE SECRET,

16:13.233 --> 16:15.887
BUT THIS IS
A PUBLIC BINDING SPELL

16:15.975 --> 16:18.455
THAT I CANSHOW YOU,
AND IT'S SIMILAR.

16:18.542 --> 16:20.501
WHAT IS YOUR NAME?WHAT'S IT TO YOU?

16:20.588 --> 16:21.763
KIMBALL CHO.HEY.

16:24.548 --> 16:26.463
GOD AND GODDESS, HEAR ME.

16:26.550 --> 16:29.249
BY LIGHT OF THE ONE FLAME,
LET THIS MORTAL SOUL,

16:29.336 --> 16:32.904
KIMBALL CHO,
BE BOUND BY MY POWER.

16:32.992 --> 16:36.212
SO THAT HE KNOWS I SPEAK TRUTH,
LET HIM BEHOLD

16:36.299 --> 16:40.042
THE KING OF BEASTS
AND KNEEL BEFORE HIM.

16:40.129 --> 16:41.391
COME ON.

16:47.093 --> 16:49.486
[speaking Latin]

16:58.365 --> 17:00.584
THAT'S IT?
THAT'S YOUR SPELL?

17:00.671 --> 17:03.805
YOU'RE NOT GONNA MAKE HIM DRINK
A POTION OR ANYTHING LIKE THAT?

17:03.892 --> 17:05.589
DOESN'T LOOK LIKE MUCH,
DOES IT?

17:05.676 --> 17:08.636
BUT IT'S VERY POWERFUL MAGIC.YEAH, OKAY.

17:08.723 --> 17:10.855
UNFORTUNATELY IT SEEMS
THAT ONE OF YOUR FRIENDS

17:10.942 --> 17:14.207
HELPED YOUR MAGIC ALONG
WITH A BLUNT INSTRUMENT.

17:14.294 --> 17:17.079
IN WHICH CASE,
YOU'RE AS UNMAGICALLY GUILTY
AS THEY ARE.

17:17.166 --> 17:19.386
IF A FRIEND OF MINE
HAD DONE THIS,

17:19.473 --> 17:23.172
