17:29.831 --> 17:32.138
THERE'S A WITCH IN TOWN. DUH.

17:32.225 --> 17:36.881
A WITCH THAT PUT A KILLING SPELL
ON THE BOY IN QUESTION.EXACTLY. IT'S PERFECT.

17:36.968 --> 17:38.579
THANK YOU FOR YOUR TIME.

17:40.711 --> 17:41.886
[Patrick] THANK YOU.

17:45.281 --> 17:48.110
CHO?
KIMBALL CHO, LET'S GO.

18:00.775 --> 18:03.473
DIDN'T WANNA BRING HER IN?YOU DON'T THINK
SHE DID THIS?

18:03.560 --> 18:05.519
