BUT ON WHAT CHARGES?

18:10.393 --> 18:12.787
SHE'S A WHACK JOB.
SHE ENJOYS THE ATTENTION.

18:12.874 --> 18:15.094
QUICKER AND MORE EFFECTIVE
TO JUST IGNORE HER

18:15.181 --> 18:18.662
AND LET HER COME TO US.THAT'S VERY ASTUTE PSYCHOLOGY,
LISBON. I'M IMPRESSED.

18:18.749 --> 18:23.798
[scoffs]WHY'D YOU GIVE HER MY NAME?
SHE SAID I WAS GONNA KNEEL

18:23.885 --> 18:26.931
BEFORE THE LORD OF BEASTS.
WHAT DOES THAT EVEN MEAN?

18:27.018 --> 18:31.153
WHAT? OH, COME ON.
YOU'RE NOT TELLING ME YOU
BELIEVE SHE'S AN ACTUAL WITCH.

18:31.240 --> 18:33.721
NO, OF COURSE NOT. BUT
IF DARK FORCES DID EXIST,

18:33.808 --> 18:36.767
IT REASONS THERE'D BE
PEOPLE WHO CONTROL THEM
FOR THEIR OWN ENDS.

18:36.854 --> 18:38.421
THEY'RE CALLED
INVESTMENT BANKERS.

18:38.508 --> 18:41.250
THEY DON'T LIVE AROUND HERE,
I ASSURE YOU. RELAX.

18:41.337 --> 18:42.512
NO SUCH THING AS WITCHES.

18:44.558 --> 18:46.560
YEAH, THAT'S EASY
FOR YOU TO SAY.

18:46.647 --> 18:48.605
WEIRD WITCH LADY
DIDN'T BURN YOU IN EFFIGY

18:48.692 --> 18:50.216
AND BIND YOU TO HER POWER.

18:58.920 --> 19:00.139
[school bell rings]

19:02.706 --> 19:05.579
"KIMBALL," SHE SAYS,
"YOU SHALL KNEEL BEFORE
THE LORD OF BEASTS."

19:05.666 --> 19:07.711
HUH. THAT'S SCARY.YEAH.

19:07.798 --> 19:11.062
YEAH, IF YOU'RE A 12-YEAR-OLD
GIRL AT HER FIRST SLEEPAWAY
CAMP.

19:11.150 --> 19:13.413
YOU HAD TO BE THERE.DON'T SWEAT IT, MAN.

19:13.500 --> 19:15.937
MET THIS GIRL IN COLLEGE.
SAID SHE WAS A WITCH.

19:16.024 --> 19:18.461
IT'S NOT A SATANIC CULT.
THEY'RE JUST NERDS IN CLOAKS.

19:20.811 --> 19:22.073
HEY, THERE HE IS.

19:25.120 --> 19:26.513
DANIEL BROWN?

19:26.600 --> 19:28.384
WE'VE GOT SOME QUESTIONS
ABOUT CODY ELKINS.

19:30.125 --> 19:31.257
[horn honks]

19:33.868 --> 19:35.870
[tires screech, horn honks]

19:35.957 --> 19:37.176
[grunts]

19:37.263 --> 19:38.873
[Daniel] NO! LET ME GO!

19:42.703 --> 19:44.661
HELLO TO BEAST.

19:44.748 --> 19:47.490
[Daniel] LET ME GO![Rigsby] COME ON.

19:47.577 --> 19:49.144
[grunting]

19:49.231 --> 19:50.624
THE SPELL WAS REAL.

19:53.627 --> 19:55.498
LET'S GO. COME ON.

20:01.069 --> 20:03.593
TELL US ABOUT YOUR FIGHT
WITH CODY ELKINS.

20:03.680 --> 20:04.942
WHAT FIGHT?

20:05.029 --> 20:06.509
THERE WAS NO FIGHT.

20:06.596 --> 20:08.946
NO? HE BEAT YOU UNCONSCIOUS
IS WHAT WE HEARD.

20:09.033 --> 20:11.427
PUT YOU IN THE HOSPITAL.
WE HAVE WITNESSES.

20:11.514 --> 20:14.735
WHO?
NAH, IT WASN'T THAT BAD.

20:14.822 --> 20:17.520
PUT YOU IN THE HOSPITAL?YEAH, FOR A COUPLE OF HOURS.

20:17.607 --> 20:18.826
IT WAS OBSERVATION.

20:21.524 --> 20:23.134
SO WHY DIDN'T YOU
PRESS CHARGES?

20:23.222 --> 20:25.441
IT WAS A MISUNDERSTANDING
BETWEEN FRIENDS.

20:25.528 --> 20:27.443
IT'S NOBODY'S FAULT.

20:27.530 --> 20:30.359
[singsong voice]
OH, I WANNA GET IN THERE.

20:30.446 --> 20:32.100
GO IN THERE.

20:32.187 --> 20:34.145
[normal voice]
JUST... I'M JUST...

20:34.233 --> 20:37.671
OR PERHAPS YOU FIGURED TO
TAKE REVENGE MORE... DIRECTLY?

20:37.758 --> 20:39.977
NAH.

20:40.064 --> 20:42.980
HOW DID THE FIGHT START,
DANIEL?

20:43.067 --> 20:47.246
OVER AT ROY T.'s PLACE
PLAYING CARDS, DRINKIN'.

20:47.333 --> 20:48.725
HIS MOM'S IN REHAB.

20:48.812 --> 20:50.771
SO HE'S GOT THE RUN
OF THE PLACE.

20:50.858 --> 20:52.947
I DID SOME TRASH-TALKIN'.
CODY GOT MAD.

20:54.905 --> 20:57.256
WE FOUGHT. HE WON.

20:57.343 --> 20:58.735
THAT'S ALL.I'M GOING IN.

21:00.346 --> 21:03.218
