21:08.919 --> 21:10.965
HI. I'M PATRICK.

21:11.052 --> 21:12.096
YOU MUST BE...DANIEL.

21:12.183 --> 21:13.576
ALRIGHT, DANIEL?YEAH?

21:13.663 --> 21:17.276
CAN I KEEP YOUR HAND? THANKS.
NOTHING STRANGE.

21:17.363 --> 21:20.540
I WANT YOU TO BREATHE...
[exhales]

21:20.627 --> 21:22.019
AND LOOK RIGHT HERE.

21:23.891 --> 21:26.502
WHAT DID YOU SAY
THAT ANGERED CODY?

21:26.589 --> 21:30.463
IT WAS A CARD GAME.
A LOT OF TRASH-TALKING.

21:30.550 --> 21:32.465
SO I WAS TRIPPING
ON HIS FAMILY LIKE,

21:32.552 --> 21:35.990
"YOUR MOM'S A HO.
DAD'S A PUNK BITCH."

21:36.077 --> 21:39.559
KEEP IT OVER HERE.
JUST RELAX AND KEEP IT
RIGHT UP IN HERE.

21:39.646 --> 21:41.865
ALRIGHT, I'M LOOKIN'
AT YOU, MAN.GOOD.

21:41.952 --> 21:45.347
ANYWAY, CODY GOES OFF.

21:45.434 --> 21:48.219
BAM. SMASHES A BEER BOTTLE
OVER MY HEAD.

21:48.307 --> 21:50.134
NO WARNING.

21:50.221 --> 21:51.919
I MEAN, I'M OUT COLD,
BUT...

21:52.006 --> 21:55.009
BUT THE GUYS TELL ME HE TRIED
TO SERIOUSLY STOMP ME OUT.

21:55.096 --> 21:58.926
AND IF THEY HADN'T GRABBED HIM,
I COULD BE DEAD.

21:59.013 --> 22:01.450
HOW MUCH DID THE ELKINS
PAY YOU FOR YOUR SILENCE?

22:06.237 --> 22:08.109
NOTHING.WANNA TRY THAT AGAIN?

22:16.770 --> 22:18.119
$1,000.

22:24.647 --> 22:27.868
YOU HAVE TO ADMIT IT'S UNCANNY.
THE LORD OF BEASTS?COINCIDENCE.

22:27.955 --> 22:30.566
PLEASE.
WHAT ARE THE CHANCES?MILLION TO ONE.

22:30.653 --> 22:33.003
THERE YOU GO.LIFE IS A MILLION TO ONE.

22:33.090 --> 22:35.354
THE UNIVERSE
IS ONE BIG COINCIDENCE.

22:35.441 --> 22:37.704
COSMICALLY IMPROBABLE
COINCIDENCES--
THEY HAPPEN ALL THE TIME.

22:37.791 --> 22:40.228
WE JUST DON'T NOTICE 'EM.OR SHE'S A WITCH.

22:40.315 --> 22:42.012
[rings doorbell]OR SHE'S A WITCH.

22:45.233 --> 22:48.018
IS SHE IN CUSTODY--
THE WITCH?

22:48.105 --> 22:49.977
NO, SIR.WHY NOT?

22:50.064 --> 22:53.546
SHE DID PUT A SPELL ON YOUR SON,
LIKE YOU SAID. YOU'RE RIGHT.

22:53.633 --> 22:56.462
BUT THAT DOESN'T CONSTITUTE
A CRIMINAL OFFENSE.

22:56.549 --> 22:59.639
THAT'S PROTECTED FREE SPEECH.SO WHY ARE YOU HERE?

22:59.726 --> 23:03.817
CODY HAD SOME VIOLENCE ISSUES
THAT WE NEED TO SPEAK ABOUT.NO.

23:03.904 --> 23:06.863
HE WAS A GOOD BOY.OH, WE'RE NOT
SAYING OTHERWISE, MA'AM.

23:06.950 --> 23:09.605
BUT IF HE HAD PROBLEMS
WITH HIS TEMPER,
THAT MIGHT HELP

23:09.692 --> 23:12.086
EXPLAIN THE CONTEXT
LEADING TO HIS DEATH.

23:12.173 --> 23:16.569
CONTEXT? IN A PIG'S EAR.
YOU'RE TRYING TO BLAME CODY
FOR HIS OWN DEATH.

23:16.656 --> 23:20.703
I HAVE A QUESTION.
IT'S ALWAYS BOTHERED ME.
WHY DO THEY CALL IT FOOTBALL?

23:20.790 --> 23:23.837
PEOPLE DON'T REALLY USE
THEIR FEET MUCH, DO THEY?

23:23.924 --> 23:26.970
ARE YOU TRYING TO BE RUDE
OR DISRESPECTFUL OR WHAT?

23:27.057 --> 23:29.364
COULD I USE YOUR BATHROOM,
PLEASE?

23:29.451 --> 23:31.627
DOWN THE HALL TO YOUR LEFT.THANKS.

23:34.238 --> 23:36.458
WHAT'S HIS PROBLEM?SORRY ABOUT THAT.

23:36.545 --> 23:38.765
DO YOU KNOW A BOY
NAMED DANIEL BROWN?NO.

23:41.071 --> 23:42.333
MICHAEL...

23:46.033 --> 23:48.122
FINE.

23:48.209 --> 23:50.820
I SEE WHERE THIS IS GOING.

23:50.907 --> 23:52.431
DANIEL AND CODY HAD A FIGHT.

24:04.791 --> 24:06.880
THERE YOU ARE.

24:06.967 --> 24:08.185
GO AWAY.

24:08.272 --> 24:10.884
I CAN'T.
I WISH I COULD.

24:10.971 --> 24:13.800
IT'S MY JOB TO HOUND PEOPLE
UNTIL I GET THE TRUTH.

24:13.887 --> 24:15.671
YEAH, WELL,
UH, GOOD LUCK WITH THAT.

24:17.412 --> 24:18.413
[sighs]

24:22.286 --> 24:23.505
NICE PLACE.

24:25.159 --> 24:28.292
MUST BE TOUGH BEING
CODY ELKINS' LITTLE BROTHER.

24:28.379 --> 24:29.468
NO.

24:32.166 --> 24:34.821
WELL... SOMETIMES.

24:34.908 --> 24:36.605
ME? I'D HATE IT.

24:36.692 --> 24:39.478
HE GETS ALL THE ATTENTION,
THE GLORY,

24:39.565 --> 24:41.044
THE GIRLS FLOCKING AROUND--
FOR WHAT?

24:41.131 --> 24:43.830
FOR RUNNING AND JUMPING
AND CATCHING A-A THING?

24:43.917 --> 24:46.180
YEAH,
MONKEYS COULD DO THAT.YEAH.

24:46.267 --> 24:48.269
MONKEYS COULD DO IT BETTER.YEAH, YOU KNOW,

24:48.356 --> 24:50.706
IF MONKEYS PLAYED FOOTBALL,

24:50.793 --> 24:52.752
THEY WOULD KICK
SOME SERIOUS JOCK BUTT.

24:55.232 --> 24:57.234
[both chuckle]

24:58.540 --> 25:00.629
ALRIGHT, I ADMIT IT.

25:00.716 --> 25:04.241
I GAVE DANIEL BROWN MONEY
TO, UH, TO KEEP HIM QUIET.

25:04.328 --> 25:06.983
CODY HAS A...

25:07.070 --> 25:10.509
HAD...A REAL SHOT
AT A COLLEGE CAREER.

25:10.596 --> 25:13.947
WOULD HAVE BEEN THE FIRST ELKINS
TO HAVE THAT CHANCE,

25:14.034 --> 25:15.426
AND WE WERE SO PROUD.

25:18.299 --> 25:22.521
BUT YOU GOTTA UNDERSTAND.
A COACH HEARS ABOUT
THESE KINDS OF RUN-INS, AND...

25:22.608 --> 25:25.611
IT WOULD HAVE
RUINED HIS CHANCES
AT ONE OF THE TOP SCHOOLS.

25:25.698 --> 25:28.004
HAD THESE RUN-INS
EVER HAPPENED BEFORE?NO.

25:28.091 --> 25:31.007
NO, OUR SON HAD
NO PROBLEM WITH VIOLENCE.

25:31.094 --> 25:32.487
IT WAS AN ISOLATED INCIDENT.

25:35.403 --> 25:36.622
WHERE'S YOUR FRIEND?

25:39.189 --> 25:40.147
I DON'T KNOW.

25:41.757 --> 25:45.456
HOW COME CODY
KILLED TAMZIN DOVE'S CAT?

25:45.544 --> 25:47.981
I-I DON'T KNOW
THAT HE DID THAT.

25:48.068 --> 25:50.374
SHE SAW HIM TAKE IT.

25:50.461 --> 25:53.464
WELL, LOOK, SHE--SHE SAW
WHAT SHE SAW, RIGHT?

25:53.552 --> 25:55.118
ALRIGHT? I-I-I DON'T KNOW.

25:59.688 --> 26:01.951
UM, IF--IF HE DID DO IT...

26:04.214 --> 26:05.607
YOU KNOW, K-KILL THE CAT...

26:08.131 --> 26:10.438
DO YOU THINK
HE DESERVED TO DIE?

26:10.525 --> 26:12.309
DO YOU?I'M ASKING YOU.

26:16.009 --> 26:18.533
HEY.HEY.

26:18.620 --> 26:21.275
YOU DON'T SPEAK TO MY SON
WITHOUT MY PERMISSION.

26:21.362 --> 26:23.843
OH. WELL, THAT'S A LITTLE WEIRD
AND CONTROLLING, BUT OKAY.

26:23.930 --> 26:26.672
DO YOU MIND IF I SPEAK
TO YOUR SON, MR. ELKINS?

26:26.759 --> 26:28.717
YES, I DO MIND.

26:28.804 --> 26:30.327
I ASKED.

26:30.414 --> 26:31.502
SEE YOU AROUND, BRAD.

26:46.822 --> 26:48.607
OH, MY GOD.
WHERE'S MY FOOD?

26:48.694 --> 26:50.347
WHAT IS THIS?

26:50.434 --> 26:54.177
THAT IS HEALTHY
AND NUTRITIOUS SNACKING.I'M GONNA DIE.

26:54.264 --> 26:56.702
[chuckles sarcastically]SERIOUSLY,
I'M ALLERGIC TO CARROTS.

26:56.789 --> 26:59.269
WELL, I'M TIRED OF THE CAR
REEKING LIKE FAST FOOD.

26:59.356 --> 27:02.229
IT'S LIKE WORKING
WITH A CATERPILLAR...
[makes chomping sounds]

27:02.316 --> 27:06.059
I CAN'T EVEN BE IN
THE SAME ROOM AS A CARROT.
I GO INTO ANAPHYLACTIC--

27:06.146 --> 27:08.714
[gags, grunts]

27:08.801 --> 27:11.151
FUNNY.

27:11.238 --> 27:12.631
[sighs] THAT'S ENOUGH.

27:14.328 --> 27:17.026
RIGSBY, COME ON.

27:17.113 --> 27:18.549
IT'S BRAD.

27:18.637 --> 27:20.900
LOOK, LOOK, LOOK, LOOK.
THERE HE IS. HE'S LEAVING.

27:26.253 --> 27:27.646
[starts engine]

27:30.649 --> 27:32.172
[beep]

27:32.259 --> 27:35.741
UGH! WHY WON'T
THIS DAMN THING LOG IN?

27:35.828 --> 27:37.264
[beep]

27:37.351 --> 27:38.744
[cell phone rings]

27:44.140 --> 27:45.620
[ring]

27:45.707 --> 27:47.274
LISBON.[Van Pelt] Hey, it's me.

27:47.361 --> 27:49.668
OH, GOOD, VAN PELT.
HOW DO I GET--Wait.

27:49.755 --> 27:52.975
WE JUST FOLLOWED THE KID
TO THE WITCH'S HOUSE.

27:53.062 --> 27:55.935
Is she with him?HE JUST WENT INSIDE.
THEY HUGGED.

27:58.285 --> 27:59.939
BRAD ELKINS
IS AT TAMZIN DOVE'S.

28:00.026 --> 28:02.855
HE HUGGED HER
AND THEN WENT INSIDE.INTERESTING.

28:02.942 --> 28:05.771
THEY SHOULD WAIT
TEN MINUTES, THEN GO IN.

28:05.858 --> 28:07.163
WHY WAIT?

28:07.250 --> 28:09.209
LET THE PLOT DEVELOP.
LET THE FRUIT RIPEN.

28:09.296 --> 28:11.777
LET THE YEAST RISE,
ET CETERA.

28:11.864 --> 28:13.909
WHAT IF HE MEANS TO DO HER HARM?

28:13.996 --> 28:19.001
WELL, IF HE WAS GONNA DO THAT,
HE'D HAVE DONE IT BY NOW.

28:19.088 --> 28:22.526
WAIT TEN MINUTES,
THEN GO IN.OKAY, BOSS.

28:22.613 --> 28:25.834
WELL?WE WAIT TEN MINUTES,
THEN WE GO IN.

28:25.921 --> 28:29.577
AND PERSONALLY, I DON'T CARE
IF WE WAIT ALL NIGHT.
WITCHCRAFT CREEPS ME OUT.

28:29.664 --> 28:32.885
IT DOESN'T BOTHER ME.
NERDS IN CLOAKS.THERE'S MORE TO IT THAN THAT.

28:32.972 --> 28:36.627
AH, IT'S JUST A SILLY
ALTERNATIVE LIFESTYLE,
LIKE "STAR TREK" OR YOGA.

28:36.715 --> 28:37.846
I DO YOGA.

28:39.892 --> 28:41.154
[clears throat]

