29:47.960 --> 29:50.614
BY BLOOD, HAS HE BEEN SULLIED.

29:50.701 --> 29:52.442
BY BLOOD, LET HIM BE CLEANSED.

29:54.009 --> 29:55.315
BY BLOOD, HAS HE BEEN...

29:55.402 --> 29:56.664
HEAR THAT?WHAT IS THAT?

29:56.751 --> 29:59.580
BY BLOOD, LET HIM BE CLEANSED.

29:59.667 --> 30:02.322
NOT YOGA. [grunts]

30:02.409 --> 30:04.585
[Rigsby] POLICE, FREEZE!
EVERYBODY STAY WHERE YOU ARE!

30:04.672 --> 30:07.327
STAY WHERE YOU ARE!
DROP THE KNIFE.STAY WHERE YOU ARE!

30:07.414 --> 30:08.937
DROP THE KNIFE.

30:09.024 --> 30:11.244
BRAD, WE'RE CBI.
YOU ALRIGHT?COME ON. LET'S GO.

30:11.331 --> 30:12.680
LET'S GO BACK.WHAT? NO!

30:12.767 --> 30:14.725
WHAT--WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOU PEOPLE, HUH?

30:14.813 --> 30:17.293
WHY CAN'T YOU
JUST LEAVE ME ALONE?COME ON, BRAD.

30:17.380 --> 30:20.340
STAY CALM, BRAD. BE PATIENT
WITH THE WAYS OF THE COWEN.

30:20.427 --> 30:21.863
EVERYBODY JUST STAY
WHERE YOU ARE.

30:37.705 --> 30:39.968
"TAMZIN DOVE."

30:40.055 --> 30:42.188
I LIKE IT.

30:42.275 --> 30:46.279
THESE FILES SAY YOUR REAL NAME
IS SARAH JONES FROM NEW JERSEY.

30:46.366 --> 30:48.498
YOUR MOTHER COMMITTED SUICIDE
WHEN YOU WERE 16.

30:48.585 --> 30:51.632
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHO YOUR FATHER IS.
YOU'RE A COLLEGE DROPOUT.

30:51.719 --> 30:54.243
YOU HAVE A HISTORY
OF MILD PSYCHIATRIC PROBLEMS,

30:54.330 --> 30:57.072
AND YOU SERVED SIX MONTHS FOR
SHOPLIFTING A FEW YEARS BACK.

31:02.251 --> 31:04.863
SARAH JONES IS DEAD.

31:04.950 --> 31:07.343
I'M TAMZIN DOVE.
I AM A PRIESTESS OF WICCA.

31:07.430 --> 31:10.346
YOU CAN'T HURT ME.OH, I DON'T WANNA HURT YOU.

31:10.433 --> 31:12.609
I IMAGINE THERE'S BEEN
ENOUGH OF THAT.

31:12.696 --> 31:15.961
I WANNA HELP YOU.
THIS IS A MURDER INVESTIGATION,

31:16.048 --> 31:19.616
SO ONE WAY OR ANOTHER,
YOU'RE LOOKING AT TROUBLE.

31:19.703 --> 31:21.183
THE GODDESS
WILL PROTECT ME.

31:24.056 --> 31:27.842
TAMZIN, THE GODDESS MAY
GIVE YOU SOLACE AND HOPE

31:27.929 --> 31:29.757
AND MEANING IN YOUR LIFE,

31:29.844 --> 31:32.281
BUT SHE CAN'T PROTECT YOU
FROM THOSE POLICE OUT THERE.

31:39.419 --> 31:41.377
BRAD'S BEEN AN APPRENTICE
OF MY COVEN

31:41.464 --> 31:45.164
SINCE LAST AUTUMN EQUINOX.
THERE'S NO CRIME IN THAT.

31:45.251 --> 31:49.168
KIND OF YOUNG TO BE
A WITCH, ISN'T IT?WE'RE ALL BORN WITCH.

31:49.255 --> 31:51.605
WE'RE ALL BORN INTO MAGIC.

31:51.692 --> 31:54.042
IT'S TAKEN FROM US
AS WE GROW UP.

31:54.129 --> 31:55.914
INTERESTING, IF TRUE.

31:58.046 --> 32:01.832
HOW DID BRAD'S PARENTS FEEL
ABOUT THIS NEW DIRECTION
IN HIS LIFE?

32:01.920 --> 32:04.531
BRAD'S PARENTS JUST...

32:04.618 --> 32:06.272
REALLY HATE WITCHES
FOR SOME REASON.

32:06.359 --> 32:09.014
I MEAN, LIKE,
MORE THAN MOST.

32:09.101 --> 32:13.192
ABOUT A MONTH AGO HIS MOM
THREATENED TO KILL ME
IF I SPOKE TO HIM AGAIN.

32:13.279 --> 32:17.022
BUT YOU DID.BRAD CAME TO ME
OF HIS OWN FREE WILL.

32:17.109 --> 32:20.025
HE WAS DRAWN TO WICCA.
I COULDN'T TURN HIM AWAY.

32:20.112 --> 32:23.071
HOW DOES HE FEEL ABOUT THE SPELL
YOU PUT ON HIS BROTHER?

32:23.158 --> 32:26.031
HE'S AT PEACE WITH IT.

32:26.118 --> 32:28.903
THAT'S WHY WE WERE CONDUCTING
THE CLEANSING RITUAL.

32:28.990 --> 32:31.166
BRAD KNOWS THE DIFFERENCE
BETWEEN THE WORLD OF MAGIC

32:31.253 --> 32:33.864
AND THE REAL WORLD.

32:33.952 --> 32:36.476
HE UNDERSTANDS
I DIDN'T KILL HIS BROTHER.

32:36.563 --> 32:39.218
MAYBE BECAUSE IN THE REAL WORLD,
BRAD DID IT.

32:39.305 --> 32:40.741
WHAT HAVE YOU GOT?

32:40.828 --> 32:43.744
BRAD'S BEEN HOSPITALIZED
TWICE IN THE LAST YEAR.

32:43.831 --> 32:45.789
BOTH TIMES THE ACCIDENT REPORT
LISTS THE CAUSE

32:45.876 --> 32:47.878
AS "ROUGHHOUSING
WITH BROTHER."

32:47.966 --> 32:49.619
THINK MAYBE BRAD
HAD ENOUGH?

32:49.706 --> 32:51.056
EVERYBODY HAS A LIMIT.

32:57.062 --> 32:58.367
[whispers] I HAVE TO GO.

33:02.589 --> 33:04.199
ME?

33:04.286 --> 33:07.637
NO! W-WHY WOULD I KILL
MY OWN BROTHER?

33:07.724 --> 33:09.161
SO HE WOULD
STOP HURTING YOU.

33:09.248 --> 33:11.337
YEAH, BUT HE NEVER HURT ME.
EVER!

33:11.424 --> 33:14.601
HE PUT YOU
IN THE HOSPITAL TWICE.

33:14.688 --> 33:17.734
ACCIDENTS.
THEY--THEY WERE ACCIDENTS. SO?

33:17.821 --> 33:20.346
SO HE DID HURT YOU. IT WAS
JUST--IT WAS ACCIDENTALLY.

33:20.433 --> 33:22.000
YEAH. I-I MEAN NO.

33:24.306 --> 33:26.569
YEAH.

33:26.656 --> 33:29.833
HE HATED THAT YOU WERE FRIENDS
WITH TAMZIN, DIDN'T HE?

33:29.920 --> 33:30.921
YES.

33:33.402 --> 33:34.882
BUT YOU NEVER GAVE HER UP.

33:38.190 --> 33:40.714
WHY?

33:40.801 --> 33:42.150
I FEEL SAFE THERE.

33:45.719 --> 33:47.199
SORRY.
CAN I HAVE A MINUTE?

33:49.244 --> 33:50.289
WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

33:58.775 --> 34:02.127
THE PARENTS ARE HERE.
YOU WANT ME TO HOLD 'EM OFF?YEAH.

34:02.214 --> 34:04.694
WAIT. NO.
LET BRAD GO WITH THEM

34:04.781 --> 34:07.741
UNTIL WE GET SOME HARD EVIDENCE
TO BEAR DOWN ON THEM.

34:07.828 --> 34:09.873
YES, BUT LET ME
TALK TO THEM FIRST.

34:24.279 --> 34:26.151
[Teresa]
PLEASE HAVE A SEAT.

34:26.238 --> 34:29.067
[Michael] I DON'T SEE
WHY YOU HAD TO DRAG HIM HERE.

34:29.154 --> 34:32.200
WE'RE SORRY
FOR ANY INCONVENIENCE.

34:32.287 --> 34:33.984
STRANGE THAT
NEITHER OF YOU TOLD US

34:34.072 --> 34:35.638
ABOUT THE CONNECTION
WITH TAMZIN DOVE.

34:38.293 --> 34:40.339
WE WERE... CONFUSED,

34:40.426 --> 34:42.950
TO BE HONEST WITH YOU.
WE DON'T UNDERSTAND

34:43.037 --> 34:45.431
BRAD'S OBSESSION
WITH WITCHCRAFT.

34:45.518 --> 34:47.302
WE WANNA UNDERSTAND,
AND WE'RE TRYING,

34:47.389 --> 34:50.392
BUT IT'S... IT'S DISTURBING

34:50.479 --> 34:53.830
AND, UH, A LITTLE EMBARRASSING,
TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH.

34:53.917 --> 34:57.399
WE'RE IN THIS TOGETHER, RIGHT?
WE'RE GONNA GET HELP.

34:57.486 --> 34:59.619
NOWADAYS THERE'S, UH, THERAPY

34:59.706 --> 35:01.751
FOR THESE KINDS
OF PROBLEMS, RIGHT?

35:01.838 --> 35:03.013
WE'LL GET THROUGH THIS.

35:04.363 --> 35:06.495
HAVE YOU CHARGED
THAT, UH, WOMAN?

35:06.582 --> 35:07.714
NO.NO?

35:09.368 --> 35:12.588
I MEAN, ISN'T IT OBVIOUS
THAT SHE DID IT--

35:12.675 --> 35:15.939
HER, ONE OF HER WEIRDO FRIENDS?
I MEAN--

35:16.026 --> 35:18.116
SHE'S HELPING US
WITH OUR INQUIRIES.

35:18.203 --> 35:20.640
SHE SWEARS SHE'S INNOCENT,
SO WE'RE HAVING HER

35:20.727 --> 35:23.512
PUT A SPELL OF REVELATION
ON THE MURDER WEAPON.

35:23.599 --> 35:24.861
A SPELL OF REVELATION?

35:26.776 --> 35:28.952
WITCHES HAVE THE POWER
OF TELEKINESIS.

35:29.039 --> 35:31.477
SHE SAYS
THAT SHE HAS A SPELL

35:31.564 --> 35:34.523
WHICH WILL RAISE THE WEAPON FROM
WHEREVER IT'S BEING CONCEALED

35:34.610 --> 35:36.090
AND REVEAL ITSELF TO US.

35:36.177 --> 35:38.092
AND YOU BELIEVE
THIS EVIL CRAP?

35:38.179 --> 35:42.618
WELL, YOU NEVER CAN TELL.
WE'RE GONNA GIVE IT A WHIRL.THAT'S INSANE.

35:42.705 --> 35:46.144
HER LAST SPELL SEEMED
TO WORK PRETTY WELL.

35:46.231 --> 35:48.755
HOW COULD YOU BE SO COLD?

35:48.842 --> 35:49.886
PRACTICE.

35:52.889 --> 35:55.805
I APOLOGIZE.
BRAD IS FREE TO GO.

35:55.892 --> 35:57.155
LET'S GO.COME ON, SON.

35:58.939 --> 36:00.158
SEE YOU, BRAD.

36:08.296 --> 36:10.516
WELL, LOOK AFTER YOURSELF,
AND IF I WERE YOU,

36:10.603 --> 36:13.693
I'D STAY VERY CLEAR
OF BRAD ELKINS FOR A WHILE.

36:13.780 --> 36:16.609
HMM. I'LL DO
AS THE GODDESS TELLS ME.

36:16.696 --> 36:19.655
WHATEVER. OH, LISTEN,
NEXT TIME YOU SPEAK TO HER,

36:19.742 --> 36:23.181
COULD YOU, UH,
PUT A GOOD WORD IN FOR ME?

36:23.268 --> 36:24.617
I WILL.

36:24.704 --> 36:25.792
THANKS.

36:28.186 --> 36:31.667
I THOUGHT YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE HER CAST A SPELL
TO FIND THE MURDER WEAPON.

36:31.754 --> 36:34.235
OH, THE SPELL'S ALREADY CAST.WHEN DID SHE CAST IT?

36:34.322 --> 36:36.019
SHE DIDN'T. I DID.

36:36.106 --> 36:38.021
YOU CAN CAST SPELLS?

36:38.108 --> 36:41.677
CHO, THERE'S NO SUCH THING
AS SPELLS.

36:41.764 --> 36:42.852
I KNOW THAT.

36:45.333 --> 36:47.117
HE, UH, REALLY IS
QUITE FREAKED OUT

36:47.205 --> 36:48.858
ABOUT THIS WITCHCRAFT MALARKEY,
ISN'T HE?

36:48.945 --> 36:50.817
UH, YEAH.

36:50.904 --> 36:54.342
WE'RE GONNA NEED TO WORK
A DOUBLE SHIFT
ON THE STAKEOUT TONIGHT.

36:54.429 --> 36:57.650
ARE YOU AT LEAST GONNA
TELL ME WHAT'S GOING ON?OH, COME ON.

36:57.737 --> 36:59.391
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S GOING ON?

36:59.478 --> 37:01.654
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHO DID THIS AND WHY?

37:01.741 --> 37:03.351
NO, BUT YOU'RE
GONNA TELL ME.

37:05.484 --> 37:06.876
HOW ABOUT I SHOW YOU?

37:13.405 --> 37:14.580
[tires screech]

37:16.190 --> 37:17.887
HERE WE GO.[turns keys in ignition]

37:17.974 --> 37:19.933
BETTER CALL CHO.[shifts gears]

37:26.026 --> 37:27.288
[tires screech]

37:36.515 --> 37:38.691
[metal clanks]

37:38.778 --> 37:40.519
[vehicle approaching]

37:46.176 --> 37:48.091
YOU'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

37:48.178 --> 37:49.267
PUT IT DOWN.

37:52.618 --> 37:55.098
[voice amplified]
THIS IS GOD SPEAKING.

37:55.185 --> 37:59.538
YOU MADE ME ANGRY, MICHAEL.
VERY ANGRY.

37:59.625 --> 38:02.758
AND YOU'RE UNDER ARR--THAT'S ENOUGH.

38:02.845 --> 38:04.020
ARREST.

38:10.244 --> 38:11.898
AMAZING, ISN'T IT?

38:11.985 --> 38:14.640
THE MURDER WEAPON REVEALED.

38:14.727 --> 38:17.686
TAMZIN'S SPELLS SEEM TO WORK.

38:17.773 --> 38:21.299
I GUESS SHE REALLY IS A WITCH.I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

38:21.386 --> 38:24.606
I'M SURE FORENSICS WILL CONFIRM
YOUR SON'S BLOOD AND TISSUE

38:24.693 --> 38:27.653
ON ONE SIDE OF THE WRENCH
AND YOUR FINGERPRINTS
ON THE OTHER.

38:27.740 --> 38:29.307
I HAVE NO KNOWLEDGE OF THAT.

38:29.394 --> 38:32.397
THEN WHY WERE YOU
TRYING TO HIDE IT?

38:32.484 --> 38:35.269
TALK TO US, MICHAEL.
MAYBE THERE WERE CIRCUMSTANCES.

38:35.356 --> 38:37.053
MAYBE YOU HAD
TO DEFEND YOURSELF.

38:37.140 --> 38:39.099
I DON'T HAVE
TO TELL YOU ANYTHING.

38:39.186 --> 38:42.537
WHAT ABOUT YOUR SONS' TRIPS
TO THE EMERGENCY ROOM--

38:42.624 --> 38:44.234
THEIR BROKEN BONES?

38:44.322 --> 38:47.063
JUST CLUMSY, I GUESS.

38:47.150 --> 38:49.327
MAYBE A LITTLE DENSE AT TIMES.

38:49.414 --> 38:52.286
GOOD THAT THEY HAD YOU
TO KEEP 'EM IN LINE, HUH?

38:52.373 --> 38:56.464
SOME PEOPLE JUST DON'T
UNDERSTAND HOW LUCKY THEY ARE.

38:56.551 --> 38:58.074
THAT'S RIGHT.

38:59.859 --> 39:01.861
I REALIZED IT WAS YOU
WHEN BRAD SAID

39:01.948 --> 39:04.603
HE LIKED GOING TO TAMZIN'S HOUSE
BECAUSE HE FELT SAFE THERE.

39:04.690 --> 39:08.258
SAFE--HE FEELS
SAFER AT A WITCH'S HOUSE

39:08.346 --> 39:09.782
THAN THEY DO AT HOME.

39:12.915 --> 39:15.135
YOU'VE BEEN ABUSING
AND BEATING YOUR WIFE AND SONS

39:15.222 --> 39:17.572
FOR YEARS, HAVEN'T YOU?NO.

39:17.659 --> 39:22.447
MY GUESS? YOU WERE SMACKIN'
BRAD AROUND A LITTLE TOO MUCH.

39:22.534 --> 39:24.318
CODY WANTED
TO PROTECT HIS BROTHER.

39:24.405 --> 39:26.233
WAS THAT IT?NO.

39:26.320 --> 39:28.278
"NO," HE SAYS.

39:28.366 --> 39:31.194
YOUR WIFE AND SON
ARE DOWN THE HALLWAY,

39:31.281 --> 39:32.674
AND THEY SAY NO, TOO.

39:35.242 --> 39:37.679
THEY KNOW WE CAUGHT HIM
THROWING AWAY THE MURDER WEAPON,

39:37.766 --> 39:41.248
AND THEY STILL DON'T BELIEVE
HE KILLED CODY.

39:41.335 --> 39:44.033
IMAGINE HOW MUCH
THEY LOVE THIS MAN

39:44.120 --> 39:46.949
TO BE IN SUCH DENIAL.

39:47.036 --> 39:49.343
CODY CONFRONTED YOU,
DIDN'T HE?

39:49.430 --> 39:51.780
HE WOULDN'T PUT UP
WITH YOUR CRAP ANYMORE...

39:51.867 --> 39:53.913
SON OF A BITCH!

39:54.000 --> 39:55.001
[grunts]

39:55.088 --> 39:58.439
COME ON!

39:58.526 --> 40:00.441
BUT YOU WOULDN'T HEAR OF IT.

40:04.489 --> 40:05.794
AAH!

40:10.233 --> 40:12.279
HE HIT ME.

40:12.366 --> 40:14.063
I WAS DEFENDING MYSELF.

40:19.939 --> 40:21.157
GOOD-BYE, MICHAEL.

40:24.813 --> 40:25.988
[door opens]

40:50.273 --> 40:53.189
[speaking inaudibly]

40:56.062 --> 40:57.977
[sobbing]

41:06.333 --> 41:08.422
MORNING.

41:08.509 --> 41:11.381
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?AH, JUST A LITTLE FAVOR
FOR CHO.

41:36.102 --> 41:39.192
UH, TAMZIN DOVE TOLD ME
TO GIVE YOU THIS.

41:39.279 --> 41:41.499
SHE SAID TO KEEP IT
IN A SAFE PLACE.

41:56.165 --> 41:58.124
STAY TUNED FOR SCENES
FROM OUR NEXT EPISODE.

42:01.823 --> 42:03.651
♪♪
